# Tools directory
# Place third-party tools and utilities here

Recommended tools to include:
- ADB (Android Debug Bridge)
- Fastboot
- Odin (Samsung)
- SP Flash Tool (MediaTek)
- QFIL/QPST (Qualcomm)
- idevice tools (iOS)
- Other proprietary unlocking tools

Note: Due to licensing, these tools are not included in the repository
and must be obtained separately.
